Oh, boy.

333
00:19:39,428 --> 00:19:40,679
Fun, huh?

334
00:19:40,763 --> 00:19:42,597
-Merry Christmas, penguins.
-(ALL QUACK)

335
00:19:45,768 --> 00:19:47,853
(SINGING)
There's something in the wind today

336
00:19:47,937 --> 00:19:49,938
that's good for everyone

337
00:19:50,523 --> 00:19:53,024
Yes, faith is in our hearts today

338
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:55,318
We're shining like the sun

